Class BeaconMessageReporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mway.bluerange.android.sdk.core.streaming.BeaconMessageStreamNode
      • com.mway.bluerange.android.sdk.core.streaming.BeaconMessagePassingStreamNode
        • com.mway.bluerange.android.sdk.core.reporting.BeaconMessageReporter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BeaconMessageStreamNodeReceiver

    public class BeaconMessageReporter
extends BeaconMessagePassingStreamNode
    A beacon message reporter periodically reads the log of a BeaconMessageLogger instance and sends reports to a specified sender. The reports will be sent to the receiver every timeBetweenReportsInMs milliseconds.
